reviews.review_text:
Grate Sounding AUD I can't believe no one else has commented on the high quality of this show. I would personally like to thank the two guys who took the time to make this sound so good. Just give a listen to Help on the Way from the other audience recordings on the Archive. 
I have only listened to the second set and it kicks major ass. Download now.

Best version This is probably the best sounding recording of all the choices for this show, if using the streamed versions is fair.  This was one fun night --very trippy at the Centrum--place had good sound to be sure.  

Have never seen a sdbd for this night.  Maybe Healy was partying too.
